babel.sty:
---------

babel.sty is taken from tetex-base package, with additional changes.

The Thai-specific changes in babel.sty are under Copyright by:

  Copyright (C) 2001-2004  Chanop Silpa-Anan <chanop@debian.org>.

The original babel.sty is generated with docstrip from babel.dtx, which is
under Copyright by:

